title: Grateful Dead Live at The Centrum on 1984-10-08

Set 1

Iko Iko, Beat It On Down The Line, Candyman, CC Rider, Bird Song, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication-> Deal

Set 2

Terrapin Station-> Samson & Delilah-> I I Just Want To Make Love To You To You-> I Need A Miracle-> Drums-> Truckin'-> Wharf Rat-> Not Fade Away, E: U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text: the centrum sounds grate! WOW!!!!!!! This just sounds so sweet.grate taper

Mind out of body! Great recording! Sat low on Brents side during set 2, very, very dosed! Some excellent jamming, esp. I just Wanna make love to you! played it twice in 84....check it at about 6:45 and the jam dips into Caution like madness! Great tour!
Insane! Never pass up an '84 show without a listen!
